    <briefdescription>
<para>USITT DMX512-A Stage &amp; Architectural Lighting Protocol Stack. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Provides non-blocking, zero-malloc DMX512 Master transmitter and Slave receiver engines supporting standard 512-channel universes, start code filtering, start address slot mapping, and UART framing breaking. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
